clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Indicated for the treatment of pediatric and adult patients with acquired methemoglobinemia Other clinical applications of methylene blue include improvement of hypotension associated with various clinical states an antiseptic in urinary tract infections treatment of hypoxia and hyperdynamic circulation in cirrhosis of liver and severe hepatopulmonary syndrome and treatment of ifofosamide induced neurotoxicity
